## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-716">Il <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> classe è obsoleta in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-716">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-717">È possibile creare un oggetto di convalida <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> istanza utilizzando il <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> classe e <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> metodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-717">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-718">Per altre informazioni, vedere la sezione Note della pagina di riferimento <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-718">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-719">L'utente deve verificare il tipo restituito.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-719">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-720">Ad esempio,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-720">For example,</span></span>  

```  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-721">Se viene eseguita la convalida di XML Schema, il `XmlSchemaType` o `XmlSchemaDatatype` corrisponde all'elemento corrente da leggere.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-721">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-722">Se viene eseguita la definizione di tipo documento (la convalida DTD), questa proprietà restituisce `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-722">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` viene restituito se l'elemento corrente, o l'attributo è un tipo semplice che è possibile specificare vincoli di convalida speciali sui tipi semplici, ad esempio min e max.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` viene restituito se l'elemento corrente, o l'attributo è un elemento simpleType definito dall'utente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` viene restituito se l'elemento corrente è un elemento complexType definito dall'utente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-726">Questo tipo non può essere restituito dagli attributi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-726">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-727">Se <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> è stata impostata alcuna informazione sul tipo di dati non è ValidationType, forniti da schemi o DTD.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-727">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  

> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="9abe1-728">Dopo la chiamata <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType restituirà Null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9abe1-728">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  



